---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout title="Legal Notice" lang={lang}>
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-premium max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-8">Legal Notice</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">Identifying Information</h2>
        <p>In compliance with Article 10 of Law 34/2002, of July 11, on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce, the owner of this website is Hanazz, based in Barcelona, Spain.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">Terms of Use</h2>
        <p>Use of this website implies full acceptance of the conditions set forth herein. Reproduction, distribution or public communication of the contents is prohibited without prior authorization.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All contents of the website, including texts, photographs and designs, are the property of Henna By Hanazz and are protected by Spanish intellectual property legislation.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-4">Applicable Law</h2>
        <p>This website is governed by Spanish law. For any dispute, the courts of Barcelona shall have jurisdiction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
